Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得找到基拉·汀斯利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要么跟血腥约翰是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么马上就要成为他下一个目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁干的  告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  她说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说血腥约翰左肩膀有个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的筹码
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:31.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}马里布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,500)\fs18\pos(193.8,204.8)}加利福尼亚  马里布  简的家宅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-简  -喂  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  别这么做  别扔下我这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  求你了  你身处险境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样做是在自寻死路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(189,132)}两天前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,132)\fad(0,400)}星期二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纹身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以用那个来确定血腥约翰的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  -太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们只要一个个检查疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看哪个人身上就纹身就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰还不知道我发现纹身的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果我们去查他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能血腥约翰会发现此事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在我们还没机会接近他的时候就销声匿迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把五名疑犯同时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合到一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再检查是否有纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何才能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就直接叫他们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他们会同意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没打算给他们选择的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成行了  还有个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布莱特·斯特尔斯因两起谋杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被联调局通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  二十多年前的悬案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都过去那么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局现在才跟进吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定是有了什么新的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-法医证据  目击证人  -那斯特尔斯在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键就是这个  没人知道他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连联调局也不知道  斯特尔斯几周前就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  但我们会找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我配合你的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你揭露血腥约翰身份的时候我要在场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我说了好的  -说是说了  但你说的肯定不算数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事没有商量的余地  简
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我百分百同意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为我之前说得够清楚了  探员们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不知道布莱特·斯特尔斯在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们也表达得很清楚了  你这说法我们不买账
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯把天眼组织的领导权留给了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他却没有告诉你他躲藏在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本说不通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯自始至终
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都将教徒的需要放在他自己之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想让我知道是因为他想保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也因为他不想被人找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不觉得布莱特·斯特尔斯担心是否会被找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来很有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯在我们这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实世界里的时间  是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我们说话的这会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在做好心理和身体上的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以摆脱我们这个物质世界的束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是非常天真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常无知的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布莱特·斯特尔斯不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是要将自己提升到一个新的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这种道行不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要非常艰难才能触碰到这种高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然我们中有人对此是无法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡  加了一份奶油  一份糖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了  拉塞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要准备好了的话鉴证小组就要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我查明他的身份  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我怕高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  有人来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰的案子有了重大突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到了一些新线索
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常重要的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  现在还不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道能信任谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道能不能信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰有一些位高权重的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  但不能在这说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八点见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要时间找一个安全的见面地点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  在哪见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到了那天再告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太扯淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经犯过很多次错误了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是低估了血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再犯这种错误了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想知道线索  就要听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是麦卡利斯特警长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警长吗  我是派翠克·简
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克  最近怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我打电话是有事想问你  -问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上个月我去纳帕谷的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说听任我的调遣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说话算数吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我是讲信用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我能指望你帮我个忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八点我需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到那天我再告诉你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于血腥约翰的事  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们准备好了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  伊夫林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这是给您的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}派翠克·简正在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚你们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将见证我升天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这个世界  飞升到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个世外的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要为我哀悼  我的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这并非逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是启程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,131)\fad(0,400)}星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  唐  你养的不是一个情妇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是一个想要报复你  会毁掉你的疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算你走运  我的工作就是解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在要做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要给她开张支票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给她很大一笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后祈祷这事就这么完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还没完  也别担心  唐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多种办法可以让一个女人闭嘴  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高兴见到你  特蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  请给我来一杯黑咖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上八点把我叫来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个调查需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么  如果你找我帮忙那这就很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  特蕾莎  我还不了解你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和简对血腥约翰的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有进展了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"也许"  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要搞得这么神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的  为什么要瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们该不会觉得我是血腥约翰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就是这么想的  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要想找我问话  那就逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则就别把我扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果问不管用  我不问了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不为加调局工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在无法得到执法人员所能得到的保护了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么  你威胁我  -不是我  是简
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他明天晚上想见你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果不去  他就会认为你是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他会找你麻烦的  雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解简的  你知道他身上发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道血腥约翰对他做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我  我不会拿这个试探他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不怕派翠克·简
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去和他见一面又有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果去了  你和简
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会再怀疑我是血腥约翰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后绝对不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没说完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是在折磨我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯特尔斯  -他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他在哪儿  -我帮不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都为天眼组织工作这么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想抓他  我只想跟他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我这个忙  算我欠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早你会需要我帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷·哈弗内说斯特尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一架私人飞机供其往来国内不被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机主是一个名叫莱恩·帕克斯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克斯  知道了  我去查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简到局里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  没见他的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(189.6,266.4)}加州  帕罗奥多  帕罗奥多机场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉莫特先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  有什么可效劳的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周探员  瑞斯比探员  加调局的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想请你回答几个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚有一架G6私人飞机降落在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注册尾号为M550MT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约十一点左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道飞机上的人是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  私人飞机不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提供乘客名单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有碰巧见到有谁从飞机上下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  有汽车服务公司的人来接他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可能帮得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会正好知道那个汽车服务公司的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汽车服务公司那边怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说昨晚从机场接到了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操着英国口音的银发男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯特尔斯  -我们也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地址是厄瓜多尔领事馆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旧金山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的  你们俩去查查看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  范佩尔  不如你一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们能利用这个优势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没有  -没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我没问题的  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-职责所在  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:16:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就干点跑腿的活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了  有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈弗内答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  斯特尔斯那边怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩尔好像瞄准他的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她正在查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就还剩一个血腥约翰案疑犯要约谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  伯特仑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正往他办公室走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-咱们那边见吗  -好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(190.8,267.2)}加利福尼亚  旧金山  厄瓜多尔领事馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾斯·范佩尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次见到你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次有何贵干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是简
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要你帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差你来  他可真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我到底能为派翠克·简做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想见见你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天晚上八点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我们上次一别  你变样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟我说你嫁给那个只会傻笑的呆子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你会去见简吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能见他我再高兴不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很乐意  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不幸的是  鉴于我现在的境况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不太能成行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说因为联邦调查局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你功课做得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不知道我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们也就不知道你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要是不肯见简  他们就会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的确变了  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去过厄瓜多尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很多很多年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那传教来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的人很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有个年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很穷  但野心勃勃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在他身上看到了些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定试着帮帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮他付学费
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也没什么  但你猜怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子已经是国务部长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很为他高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他邀请我住在这豪华的领事馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这一片小小的外国领土上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外国领土  如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不受你们加调局  联调局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与任何美国法律管辖的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  格蕾斯  你的威胁不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  很高兴能再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我跟简问个好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去的时候随手关门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啊  我感觉轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  案子有突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么案子  -血腥约翰案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上就能确定凶手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的确定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你们有了切实答案要立刻告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此案结束的时候我要在场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等您这句话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚和派翠克·简谈了点有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特仑那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了  斯特尔斯那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不太好  -你找到他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住在厄瓜多尔领事馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他在里面  我们就动不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来对付斯特尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会也不必跟你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我的说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霰弹枪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火力够大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于明天晚上的事  我们得谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经告诉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先听我说完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望我在场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望我在场是因为你觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会阻止你杀血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是你不会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像血腥约翰这种禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本连上庭受审的资格都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种人就该就地正法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  让我搞搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在执法部门干了快二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然就这么改变原则了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在血腥约翰案上吗  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很惊讶  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你不相信我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我认识的最诚实的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情上  你绝不会骗我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明晚见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明晚见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,131)\fad(0,400)}星期四
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  我亲爱的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近来还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  那么说你不是来找我聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明晚八点你要来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-派翠克  -不  你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你明晚八点来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则等到我再回来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.66,0:24:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这是领事馆也保不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.08,0:24:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.62,0:24:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的话句句当真
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.49,0:24:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.23,0:24:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将死之人还怕什么死亡威胁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.14,0:24:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装模作样骗骗你那些信徒还行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.31,0:24:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗我就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.22,0:24:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太高估我了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.68,0:24:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常不幸的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.94,0:24:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不是装的了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.16,0:24:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还剩多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.77,0:24:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经扩散到血液了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.12,0:24:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无药可医了  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.69,0:24:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许两周  也许一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.23,0:24:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.74,0:24:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是针对你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.82,0:24:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.78,0:25:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间对我来说太宝贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.39,0:25:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我还是需要你来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.88,0:25:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.90,0:25:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事如此重要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.34,0:25:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.00,0:25:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于接近他了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.73,0:25:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前所未有的接近
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.03,0:25:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.29,0:25:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.49,0:25:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我若能去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.21,0:25:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是再高兴不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.35,0:25:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.32,0:25:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的情况比你想象的复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.18,0:25:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被困在这儿还有别的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.68,0:25:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.24,0:25:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  事实正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.08,0:25:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟我到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.80,0:25:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等着我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.52,0:25:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我想呆在这儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.51,0:25:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.75,0:25:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说联调局是唯一的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.15,0:25:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意  前门有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.23,0:26:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天眼组织的车
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.63,0:26:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在偷偷往外转移什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.78,0:26:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时准备行动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.84,0:26:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即行动  行动  上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.58,0:26:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不许动  -不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.35,0:26:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在方向盘上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.71,0:26:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在我们能看见的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.66,0:26:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好  先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.39,0:26:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么能为你们效劳的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.83,0:27:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯入局了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.69,0:27:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.64,0:27:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可有很长一段车程
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.88,0:27:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他带走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.16,0:27:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}晚上八点  马里布  雪松街1309号见  走便道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.42,0:27:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}信息已发送
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.02,0:27:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么萨城警局只有等着了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.78,0:27:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想用职权压人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.52,0:27:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若有必要我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.98,0:28:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯文  回头我再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.36,0:28:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.69,0:28:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.23,0:28:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看日落
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.20,0:29:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本  有些话我想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.22,0:29:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很早以前就应该跟你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.16,0:29:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.51,0:29:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚点再谢也不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.67,0:29:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.31,0:29:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须现在就说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.20,0:29:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.81,0:29:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你对我意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.51,0:29:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.73,0:30:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.19,0:30:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点忘了  我有个惊喜给你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.73,0:30:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这等我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.31,0:30:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.35,0:31:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}马里布
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.65,0:31:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(191.4,268)}加利福尼亚  马里布  简的家宅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.53,0:34:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.10,0:34:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请停车
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.32,0:34:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.48,0:34:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是加州调查局探员
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.83,0:34:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我要征用你的车
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.13,0:34:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.19,0:34:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.03,0:34:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即下车  快
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.15,0:34:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.80,0:34:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.51,0:34:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要报警
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.88,0:34:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.58,0:35:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-简  -喂  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.64,0:35:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  别这么做  别扔下我这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.23,0:35:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.60,0:35:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  求你了  你身处险境
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.27,0:35:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.40,0:35:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.18,0:35:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.11,0:35:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样做是在自寻死路
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.27,0:35:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.21,0:35:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.56,0:35:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.69,0:36:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.67,0:37:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来早了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.06,0:37:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不早  来得正好  坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.57,0:37:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,911  您遇到了什么紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.48,0:37:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是加州调查局的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.85,0:37:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾莎·里斯本探员
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.65,0:37:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请派警员到马里布的雪松街1309号
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.69,0:37:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有探员需要立即支援
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.42,0:37:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你们五个聚在一起是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.55,0:37:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人可能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.87,0:37:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人可能猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.88,0:37:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们中的一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.27,0:37:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.96,0:37:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  在我们几个中间
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.57,0:37:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们其中之一是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.55,0:37:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.02,0:37:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是谁  -我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.08,0:38:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到这来就是为了找出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.27,0:38:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想说这个房间里的某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.39,0:38:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个连环杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.56,0:38:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我很确定  -太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.96,0:38:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证完全不荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.16,0:38:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证  我才不跟你在这儿胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.43,0:38:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.25,0:38:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步都别想往门口走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.74,0:38:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不准走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.62,0:38:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放轻松  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.25,0:38:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看起来很紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.33,0:38:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.57,0:38:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.38,0:38:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.97,0:38:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢把你们的枪拿出来  放在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.08,0:38:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推到我这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.18,0:38:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.71,0:38:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.11,0:39:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.32,0:39:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.71,0:39:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.54,0:39:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这才刚刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.52,0:39:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这一刻  我等了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.80,0:39:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多年来  血腥约翰一直很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.65,0:39:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们中的某个人一直很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.86,0:39:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很谨慎  除了这次
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.57,0:39:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一次  你露出马脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.72,0:39:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基拉·汀斯利死之前跟我说了件事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.66,0:39:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她告诉我杀她的人  也就是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.10,0:39:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.02,0:39:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三个点
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.71,0:39:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在肩膀上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.77,0:39:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都得
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.41,0:39:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.48,0:39:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻动手
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.99,0:39:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始脱吧  快
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.86,0:39:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.22,0:40:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.84,0:40:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.89,0:40:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想得那样
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.29,0:40:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你弄错了  -住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.47,0:40:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.71,0:40:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  等等  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.83,0:40:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.40,0:40:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.54,0:41:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.21,0:41:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到他们俩那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.10,0:41:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别动
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.23,0:41:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你们三个
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.40,0:41:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到墙边站着  快
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.20,0:41:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.58,0:41:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}马里布
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.51,0:42:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
